{"format": "tiptap/v1", "updatedAt": "2026-06-21T15:50:59.863Z", "doc": {"type": "doc", "content": [{"type": "image", "attrs": {"src": "data:image/svg+xml;base64,", "alt": "Conflict Resolution — concept overview"}}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "What It Is"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Conflict Resolution in Git"}, {"type": "text", "text": " is the process of manually reconciling changes when two branches modify the same part of a file differently, causing Git to flag a "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "merge conflict"}, {"type": "text", "text": " because it can't automatically decide which version to keep. In modern software engineering workflows, this happens within a structured pipeline: you create a "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "feature branch"}, {"type": "text", "text": ", submit a "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "pull request (PR)"}, {"type": "text", "text": " for merging, and undergo "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "code review"}, {"type": "text", "text": " before your changes enter the main codebase."}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Why It Matters"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Merge conflicts are inevitable in collaborative development. Without proper resolution:\n- Code integration stalls, blocking team progress\n- Incorrect changes might be merged, introducing bugs\n- Team coordination breaks down when multiple developers edit the same files"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Proper conflict resolution ensures "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "code quality"}, {"type": "text", "text": ", "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "team collaboration"}, {"type": "text", "text": ", and "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "continuous integration"}, {"type": "text", "text": " flow smoothly."}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Benefits"}]}, {"type": "table", "content": [{"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Benefit"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Impact"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Clean codebase"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Prevents broken builds and regression bugs"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Team alignment"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Ensures all developers understand changes"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Reviewable history"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Maintains clear commit history for future debugging"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Early bug detection"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Code review catches issues before merge"}]}]}]}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Trade-offs"}]}, {"type": "table", "content": [{"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Limitation"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Consequence"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Time cost"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Resolution can take 15–60+ minutes for complex conflicts"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Human judgment required"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "AI can suggest but 